    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The validation evidence from the Morrison bench study demonstrates CFD predictions are within acceptable tolerance of measured haemolysis values across the full operating envelope. The six non-assessed factors are judged not applicable or acceptable by scope exclusion at MRL 2. The assessment team concluded that the body of evidence, including the bench validation activity, is sufficient to support the Accepted decision for this COU.",
    "decidedAt": "2026-04-19T00:00:00Z"
